author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
Big changes are coming to The Elder Scrolls Online, and you can learn all about them during our 2026 Reveal. Tune in to our Seasons Announce as the ESO Leadership and Community Teams usher in a new age for The Elder Scrolls Online with YOU.  We’ll be revealing all the new content, changes, and player-focused improvements coming in 2026 (and beyond).

title: The Elder Scrolls Online - 2026 Reveal
